  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with dizziness presently undergo physical therapy rehabilitation. Our study will
      study whether Wii Balance Board made by Nintendo Inc. will be helpful in patients with
      dizziness. They will undergo dizziness evaluation to quantify their dizziness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
